						TO INSTALL INSTALL & WORDPRESS ON LOCAL HOST
						
						
Step 1)
	Install Xampp on local server. (Video link- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R5CUn5wGQGg )
	
Step 2)
	Install and configure Wordpress. (Video link- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RtXA60HewUw&list=PLjVLYmrlmjGfC44WZSTvlsZFzxnQsysJb&index=3 )
	
Step 3)
	To download themes, it will require a FTP User. (Made from this artiicle:- https://linuxconfig.org/how-to-setup-and-use-ftp-server-in-ubuntu-linux )
	In this case:- ftp username- ftpuser
		       password	   - a
	
	
	
